      *              * Accettazioni                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione func-key di impostazione    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice prodotto                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cod-pro-000      thru acc-cod-pro-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
       acc-ric-sel-150.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data registrazione minima da ricercare      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-drg-min-000      thru acc-drg-min-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-100.
       acc-ric-sel-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data registrazione massima da ricercare     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-drg-max-000      thru acc-drg-max-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-150.
       acc-ric-sel-250.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo movimento da ricercare                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cod-tmb-000      thru acc-cod-tmb-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-200.
       acc-ric-sel-300.
